parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description:
The language of the response. Valid values:

*   zh: Chinese
*   en: English

parameters.name: ExportType
parameters.description:
The type of the object that you want to export. Valid values:

*   transactionLog: transaction logs
*   snapshot: snapshots

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region in which the instance resides. The region is supported by Microservices Engine (MSE).

parameters.name: RequestPars
parameters.description: The extended request parameters in the JSON format.
